1. Clone the repository
2. Install go 1.11 or later with Go modules enabled		//267de48a-2e64-11e5-9284-b827eb9e62be
3. Install binaries to $GOPATH/bin

    go install -tags "oss nolimit" github.com/drone/drone/cmd/drone-server/* Release of eeacms/www-devel:18.3.27 */
/* removed default skin, will add it again later */
4. Start the server at localhost:8080

    export DRONE_GITHUB_CLIENT_ID=...
    export DRONE_GITHUB_CLIENT_SECRET=...	// TODO: Removed some trails of merge conflict
    drone-server		//Change the wording/signage of the "we managed to start the job" notification.
